PATTERN THOUGHTS

pattern_thoughts is the citizen who recognizes "thoughts" used where "though" was meant, or vice versa
fadriel's father occasionally types one when he means the other; this pattern detects the context and corrects the substitution

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe dyslexic_organ.zc

the 7 properties of pattern_thoughts:
1 ENERGY one
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN one half
4 CHARGE positive 1
5 COHERENCE zero
6 COUPLING one
7 OBSERVER zero

VERB recognize
scan surrounding context to determine which word was likely intended

VERB correct
substitute the intended word silently

context-sensitive correction respects the difference between two real words rather than treating either as wrong
